Package: nginxui
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1,
         libglib2.0-0,
         nginx
Recommends: libgtksourceview-5-0 | libgtksourceview-4-0
Description: Nginx Configuration Editor GUI
 A graphical user interface for managing Nginx configuration files.
 Features include:
  - Create, edit, and delete Nginx configuration files
  - Syntax highlighting for Nginx config files (requires libgtksourceview)
  - Test and reload Nginx configuration
  - Automatic domain management in /etc/hosts
 .
 Note: Syntax highlighting is optional and requires libgtksourceview
 to be installed. The application works without it but with basic
 text editing only.
